        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>简易计算器</strong></p><p>只包括了加减乘除的运算</p><p>首先我们要从键盘获取数字和运算符，初始化</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">Scanner</span> <span class="variable">sc</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Scanner</span>(System.in);</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;请输入首位数字&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">double</span> newNum;</span><br><span class="line">newNum = sc.nextDouble();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后我们要想的，当我输入第一位数字和第二位数字并进行运算后，得到的是第一对的运算结果 </p><p>再次进行运算时，进行操作的数值为第二位数字和第一对的运算结果进行运算，以此类推，在进行第一次运算后，每当我们再次进行运算后。拿取的值都为上一次运算结果的第二位数字和上一次的运算结果</p><p>所以，为了获取每一次的运算结果值，我们要在main函数的首部创建一个动态数组，用来存储数值</p><p>为了获取动态数组的每一个索引，我们创建一个变量</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ArrayList&lt;Double&gt; numArr = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ArrayList</span>&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">count</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来获取键盘中的运算符,考虑到可能进行多次运算，我们设置一个循环，并定义退出条件</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;按e退出运算&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    String cal;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="literal">true</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;请输入运算符&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    cal = sc.next();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(cal.equals(<span class="string">&quot;e&quot;</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.exit(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(!cal.equals(<span class="string">&quot;+&quot;</span>) &amp;&amp; !cal.equals(<span class="string">&quot;-&quot;</span>) &amp;&amp; !cal.equals(<span class="string">&quot;*&quot;</span>) &amp;&amp;! cal.equals(<span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;运算符输入有误，请重新输入&quot;</span>);   </span><br><span class="line">   &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>获取参加运算的第二位数字,获取完对索引进行增加</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">double</span> oldNum;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第二位数字&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    oldNum = sc.nexDouble();</span><br><span class="line">    count++;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运算方法</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="type">double</span> <span class="title function_">add</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">double</span> newNumber, <span class="type">double</span> oldNumber)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">return</span> newNumber + oldNumber;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="type">double</span> <span class="title function_">sub</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">double</span> newNumber, <span class="type">double</span> oldNumber)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">return</span> newNumber - oldNumber;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="type">double</span> <span class="title function_">mul</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">double</span> newNumber, <span class="type">double</span> oldNumber)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">return</span> newNumber * oldNumber;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>除数不能为0,对此进行判断</p><p>注意，如果我将分子输入了0，数值会返回0</p><p>这样的话是不合法的运算，然而我们也会将count自增，从而导致动态数组的索引值发生错乱</p><p>所以我们要返回第二位数字输入的位置，增加个判断</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="type">double</span> <span class="title function_">dev</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">double</span> newNumber, <span class="type">double</span> oldNumber)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">if</span> (oldNumber != <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="keyword">return</span> newNumber / oldNumber;</span><br><span class="line">       &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果返回值为0，count不进行自增，并提示重输，直到运算为合法的</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="literal">true</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;请输入数字&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">              oldNum = sc.nextDouble();</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">if</span> (dev(newNum, oldNum) != <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                  count++;</span><br><span class="line">                  <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">              &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                  System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;数值输入有误,请重新输入&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">              &#125;</span><br><span class="line">          &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接下来判断符号并进行对结果的输出</p><p>if()判断是否为第一次进行运算</p><p>如果是将第一次的运算结果添加到动态数组中，方便之后运算的取值，此时的索引值为0</p><p>如果不是，要获取上一次的运算结果，也就是numArr[0]</p><p>由于我们每输入第二个数字后，count都会自增</p><p>所以我们第一次输出运算结果时的索引值为1，第二次及之后索引值必然时大于等于2 的</p><p>为了进行运算，要获取上一次结果的值，所以要使动态数组的索引值-2拿值</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">switch</span> (cal) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;+&quot;</span> -&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                  <span class="keyword">if</span> (count == <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                      numArr.add(add(newNum, oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;结果为&quot;</span> + add(newNum, oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                  &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                      numArr.add(add(numArr.get(count - <span class="number">2</span>), oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;结果为&quot;</span> + add(numArr.get(count - <span class="number">2</span>), oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">              &#125;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;-&quot;</span> -&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                  <span class="keyword">if</span> (count == <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                      numArr.add(sub(newNum, oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;结果为&quot;</span> + sub(newNum, oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                  &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                      numArr.add(sub(numArr.get(count - <span class="number">2</span>), oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;结果为&quot;</span> + sub(numArr.get(count - <span class="number">2</span>), oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">              &#125;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;*&quot;</span> -&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                  <span class="keyword">if</span> (count == <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                      numArr.add(mul(newNum, oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;结果为&quot;</span> + mul(newNum, oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                  &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                      numArr.add(mul(numArr.get(count - <span class="number">2</span>), oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;结果为&quot;</span> + mul(numArr.get(count - <span class="number">2</span>), oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">              &#125;</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span> -&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                  <span class="keyword">if</span> (count == <span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                      numArr.add(dev(newNum, oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;结果为&quot;</span> + dev(newNum, oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                  &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                      numArr.add(dev(numArr.get(count - <span class="number">2</span>), oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;结果为&quot;</span> + dev(numArr.get(count - <span class="number">2</span>), oldNum));</span><br><span class="line">                  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">              &#125;</span><br><span class="line">          &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可能多次进行运算并输出结果，所以我们从输入符号的位置添加个循环</p><p>最终程序</p><p> public static void main(String[] args) {<br>        ArrayList<Double> numArr &#x3D; new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();<br>        Scanner sc &#x3D; new Scanner(System.in);<br>        int count &#x3D; 0;<br>        double newNum;<br>        System.out.println(“按e退出”);<br>        System.out.println(“请输入数字”);<br>        newNum &#x3D; sc.nextDouble();<br>&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;多次进行运算<br>        while (true) {<br>            String cal;<br>            while (true) {<br>                System.out.println(“请输入符号”);<br>                cal &#x3D; sc.next();<br>                if (cal.equals(“e”)) {<br>                    System.exit(0);<br>                } else if (!cal.equals(“+”) &amp;&amp; !cal.equals(“-“) &amp;&amp; !cal.equals(“<em>“) &amp;&amp; !cal.equals(“&#x2F;“)) {<br>                    System.out.println(“符号输入有误，请重新输入”);<br>                } else {<br>                    break;<br>                }<br>            }<br>            double oldNum;<br>            while (true) {<br>                System.out.println(“请输入数字”);<br>                oldNum &#x3D; sc.nextDouble();<br>                if (dev(newNum, oldNum) !&#x3D; 0) {<br>                    count++;<br>                    break;<br>                } else {<br>                    System.out.println(“有误”);<br>                }<br>            }<br>&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;运算符判断并输出结果<br>            switch (cal) {<br>                case “+” -&gt; {<br>                    if (count &#x3D;&#x3D; 1) {<br>                        numArr.add(add(newNum, oldNum));<br>                        System.out.println(“结果为” + add(newNum, oldNum));<br>                    } else {<br>                        numArr.add(add(numArr.get(count - 2), oldNum));<br>                        System.out.println(“结果为” + add(numArr.get(count - 2), oldNum));<br>                    }<br>                }<br>                case “-“ -&gt; {<br>                    if (count &#x3D;&#x3D; 1) {<br>                        numArr.add(sub(newNum, oldNum));<br>                        System.out.println(“结果为” + sub(newNum, oldNum));<br>                    } else {<br>                        numArr.add(sub(numArr.get(count - 2), oldNum));<br>                        System.out.println(“结果为” + sub(numArr.get(count - 2), oldNum));<br>                    }<br>                }<br>                case “</em>“ -&gt; {<br>                    if (count &#x3D;&#x3D; 1) {<br>                        numArr.add(mul(newNum, oldNum));<br>                        System.out.println(“结果为” + mul(newNum, oldNum));<br>                    } else {<br>                        numArr.add(mul(numArr.get(count - 2), oldNum));<br>                        System.out.println(“结果为” + mul(numArr.get(count - 2), oldNum));<br>                    }<br>                }<br>                case “&#x2F;“ -&gt; {<br>                    if (count &#x3D;&#x3D; 1) {<br>                        numArr.add(dev(newNum, oldNum));<br>                        System.out.println(“结果为” + dev(newNum, oldNum));<br>                    } else {<br>                        numArr.add(dev(numArr.get(count - 2), oldNum));<br>                        System.out.println(“结果为” + dev(numArr.get(count - 2), oldNum));<br>                    }<br>                }<br>            }<br>        }<br>    }<br>&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;&#x2F;运算方法</p><p>​    public static double add(double newNumber, double oldNumber) {<br>​        return newNumber + oldNumber;<br>​    }</p><p>​    public static double sub(double newNumber, double oldNumber) {<br>​        return newNumber - oldNumber;<br>​    }</p><p>​    public static double mul(double newNumber, double oldNumber) {<br>​        return newNumber * oldNumber;<br>​    }</p><p>​    public static double dev(double newNumber, double oldNumber) {<br>​        if (oldNumber !&#x3D; 0) {<br>​            return newNumber &#x2F; oldNumber;<br>​        } else {<br>​            return 0;<br>​        }<br>  }</p><p>如果我们要将输入数字位显示异常判断，自行添加if</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
